{"tid":11782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張德江指港獨只是少數人 鼓吹市民與港獨「鬥爭」⚔️","createTime":"2016-11-29T11:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T12:54:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"070d31ebdb6761bb547152b84fff4cd46c3a8ade","tid":11782,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"為阻止青年新政游蕙禎和梁頌恆再宣誓就職立法會議員，特首梁振英借律政司入稟，司法覆核二人議員資格；人大委員長張德江更未待本港法院宣判，主動提出釋法，被指向法院施壓，遭不少人強烈質疑。張德江在北京接見「反佔中大旗手」周融及其組織「幫港出聲」時，形容港獨禍國殃民，相信廣大市民會認清港獨本質，「堅持與港獨者鬥爭」。<br />\n<br />\n張德江指，別以為港獨只是少數人提出，視而不見，一旦發展起來，「首先吃虧的、首先倒霉的，是香港同胞」，人大釋法則充份表現中央堅定反港獨、維持國家安全和一國兩制的決心和意志，並獲廣大香港市民和全國人民擁護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55981453&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55981453%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161129&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=bd943764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55981453%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161129&h=38ec8c9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55981453&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161129</a>"},{"pid":"8308f8fb6659a54d93036edccf7979296661c977","tid":11782,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"文革is ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話班廢老係避共狗先落嚟香港既，而家結果咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e341118d615e7833e127e6dce3625f447927d7","tid":11782,"uid":10100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"隻白頭公公幾時死?<img src=\"/assets/face